data.description: This is a lovely 2br 1.5 bath, open space design is located on a tree lined street in the quiet neighborhood of Station North. Tool library a block away, classes at two locations, including co-working spaces. Walking distance to transportation hub and area college shuttles. Catch the free bus and water taxi  to work or entertainment from Penn Station. Food and entertainment a few blocks away. Serious Investors with clients are welcome to view property. If no one was available previously please feel free to contact me immediately for viewing!
data.whatILove: First floor makes this house easier to set living room and dining space. Cable is pre wired and ceiling fans were installed last year for less energy consumption during fall and spring. Restaurants are close but not too close to be bothered when you need to shut the entertainment out. My kids attended Montessori charter up the street and a few students we know decided to enroll in design school for middle and high school. There’s an additional room in basement used for multiple uses, I.e. music room w/ barely any sound to outside or neighbors, playroom/home gym. There is 4 feet high storage behind utilities(cemented)! We love this home and all of our neighbors are kind, giving, considerate and caring!
